camConstuctionSetParams 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: Sets construction camera parameters.  
Syntax:  
 camera camConstuctionSetParams [[x,y,z], radius, max above land] 
Parameters: 
camera: Object 
[[x,y,z], radius, max above land]: Array 
[x,y,z]: Position 
radius: Number 
max above land: Number 
Return Value: 
 Nothing